#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-system.xml:163
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You now have to install a Portage snapshot, a collection of files that inform\n"
"Portage what software titles you can install, which profiles are available, etc.\n"
"The contents of this snapshot will be extracted to <path>/usr/portage</path>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><p>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-system.xml:169
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"We recommend the use of <c>emerge-webrsync</c>. This will fetch the latest\n"
"portage snapshot (which Gentoo releases on a daily basis) from one of our mirrors\n"
"and install it onto your system.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'caption' of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-system.xml:174
#, no-wrap
msgid "Running emerge-webrsync to install a Portage snapshot"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><body><pre>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-system.xml:175
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# <i>mkdir /usr/portage</i>\n"
"# <i>emerge-webrsync</i>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><subsection><title>
#: en/handbook/hb-install-system.xml:182
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Optional: Updating the Portage tree"
